{"_id":"HJ7qV1W0EPKxY2PZ","name":"Rain of Blows","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Attack roll Bonus:[[floor(@classes.dancer.lvl/3-1)]]</p>\n<p>Dodge AC Bonus:[[floor(@classes.dancer.lvl/3-1)]]</p>\n<p>Reflex Bonus: [[floor(@classes.dancer.lvl/3-1)]]</p>\n<p>At 6th level, while performing a battle dance, a dancer can speed up her attacks. When making a full attack action, she may make one extra attack with unarmed strikes, weapons with the &ldquo;monk&rdquo; special feature or a bladed scarf, as though under the effects of a <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/h/haste/\">haste</a> spell. She also gains a +1 bonus on attack rolls and a +1 dodge bonus to AC and on Reflex saves. At 9th level, and every three dancer levels thereafter, these bonuses increase by +1, to a maximum of +5 at 18th level. These bonuses do not stack with the haste spell.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Haste"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Dancer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"identifiedName":"Rain of Blows","size":"med","range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.1.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667698093101,"modifiedTime":1673651489974,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_kn9ouzr4hk"}}}
{"_id":"HaRtk5eBLrkocXaS","name":"Mystic Dance: Stutter Step","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite(s):</strong> Box Step<br /><br />A dancer can perform a dance that lowers the magical or elemental (chosen when afflicting a creature) resistances of a creature within 30 feet. A creature within range must make a Will save (DC 10 + half of the dancer&rsquo;s level + her Charisma modifier) or suffer a -2 penalty to spell or elemental resistance plus an additional -2 penalty per four dancer levels after 2nd for a duration of 1 round + 1 round per two dancer levels after 2nd.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Elemental Resist Down: [[floor((@classes.dancer.lvl+2)/4)*-2]]</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Mystic Dance"],["Debuff"]],"actions":[{"_id":"t6vufFkv3Rxfl4Ws","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"floor(@classes.dancer.lvl/2)","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":"30","units":"ft","maxIncrements":"1","minValue":null,"minUnits":"melee"},"uses":{"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"day","value":0,"maxFormula":"@resources.kiPool.value","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"save","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":""},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":"","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"@abilities.cha.mod + floor(@classes.dancer.lvl/2) + 10","type":"will","description":"Negate the spell/elemental resist down."},"effectNotes":[],"attackNotes":[],"soundEffect":"","powerAttack":{"multiplier":"","dam