{"_id":"L8UniPMdv0Xp9MiO","name":"Unarmed Strike","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 1st level, a dancer gains <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/feats/combat-feats/improved-unarmed-strike-combat-final/\">Improved Unarmed Strike</a> as a bonus feat. A dancer may attack with fists, elbows, knees, and feet. This means that a dancer may make unarmed strikes with her hands full. A dancer applies her full Strength modifier (not half) on damage rolls for all her unarmed strikes. Usually, a dancer&rsquo;s unarmed strikes deal lethal damage, but she can choose to deal nonlethal damage instead with no penalty on her attack roll. She has the same choice to deal lethal or nonlethal damage while grappling. A dancer&rsquo;s unarmed strike is treated as both a manufactured weapon and a natural weapon for the purpose of spells and effects that modify either manufactured weapons or natural weapons.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table id=\"tablepress-254\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-254 medium-width\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-254-name\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n<th class=\"column-1\">Level</th>\n<th class=\"column-2\">Damage (Small)</th>\n<th class=\"column-3\">Damage (Medium)</th>\n<th class=\"column-4\">Damage (Large)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"row-2\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">1st &ndash; 3rd</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">1d4</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">1d6</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">1d8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">4th &ndash; 7th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">1d6</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">1d8</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">2d6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">8th &ndash; 11th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">1d8</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">1d10</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">2d8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">12th &ndash; 15th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">1d10</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">2d6</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">3d6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">16th &ndash; 19th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">2d6</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">2d8</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">3d8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">20th</td>\n<td class=\"column-2\">2d8</td>\n<td class=\"column-3\">2d10</td>\n<td class=\"column-4\">4d8</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Feat"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Dancer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"identifiedName":"Unarmed Strike","size":"med","range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.1.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667698093111,"modifiedTime":1673651390822,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_kn9ouzr4hk"}}}
{"_id":"LGfeg425BCqKptAQ","name":"Fleet","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>While performing a battle dance, a dancer gains a +10 enhancement bonus to her land speed. This bonus increases by 5 feet for every four dancer levels gained after 1st level, to a maximum of +30 feet at 17th level.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">This gains a total of [[min(floor((@classes.dancer.lvl+3)/4) * 5 + 5, 30)]] feet while performing a battle dance.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Signika, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-hybrid_dancer.TpD5yMJsaOjOqzQ0]{Dancer: Fleet}</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Movement"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Dancer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"identifiedName":"Fleet","size":"med","range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.1.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667698093114,"modifiedTime":1673652430635,"lastModifiedBy":"VNk1dF8h7rdEhEd4"},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_kn9ouzr4hk"}}}
{"_id":"MAEhiUVtFuXUMB2N","name":"Evasion","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 2nd level, a dancer gains evasion. If exposed to any effect that normally allows her to attempt a Reflex saving throw for half damage, she takes no damage with a successful saving throw. The evasion ability can only be used if the dancer is wearing no armor (<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/equipment/armor/dancing-scarves/\">dancing scarves</a> are exempt from this).</p>\n<p><strong>Improvement at Level 12</strong></p>\n<p>This ability, gained at 12th level, works like evasion (see above). A dancer takes no damage at all on successful saving throws against attacks that allow a Reflex saving throw for half damage. What&rsquo;s more, she takes only half damage even if she fails her saving throw.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Defensive"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"If she makes a successful Reflex saving throw against an attack that normally deals half damage on a successful save and has no armor (Aside from Dancing Scarves), she instead takes no damage.","subTarget":"ref"},{"text":"At 12th level, If she fails the reflex save, she only takes half damage.","subTarget":"ref"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Dancer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"identifiedName":"Evasion","size":"med","range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"s