{"_id":"eSw2ODDuIKbrS11F","name":"Uncanny Dodge","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, a dancer cannot be caught flat-footed, even if the attacker is invisible. She still loses her Dexterity bonus to AC if immobilized. A dancer with this ability can still lose her Dexterity bonus to AC if an opponent successfully uses the feint action against her. If a dancer already has uncanny dodge from a different class, she automatically gains improved uncanny dodge (see below) instead.</p>\n<p><strong>This ability upgrades at Level 8!</strong></p>\n<p>At 8th level and higher, dancer can no longer be flanked. This defense denies a thief the ability to sneak attack the dancer by flanking her, unless the attacker has at least four more thief levels than the target has dancer levels. If a character already has uncanny dodge from another class, the levels from the classes that grant uncanny dodge stack to determine the minimum thief level required to flank the character.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Defense"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":{},"dictionary":{}},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Dancer"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"identifiedName":"Uncanny Dodge","size":"med","range":{"maxIncrements":1}},"img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"systemId":"ffd20","systemVersion":"10.1.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1667698093161,"modifiedTime":1673651485099,"l