{"_id":"hg0wJtEAEXQD0BBO","name":"Dancer’s Strike","type":"feat","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 6th level, the magic of the dancer&rsquo;s arcane maneuvers allows her to manifest auras of energy around her feet and hands. These auras can defeat an opponent&rsquo;s damage reduction. The dancer can generate this aura as a standard action at will. It persists for a number of rounds equal to 5 + the dancer&rsquo;s Charisma modifier before it fades.</p>\n<p>At 6th level, the dancer&rsquo;s aura makes her unarmed strikes count as magic damage.</p>\n<p>At 12th level, the dancer chooses one aspect of her alignment, such as good or chaotic. Her aura allows her strikes to count as that alignment (as well as magic). She must choose one aspect of her alignment, and once she has made a choice she cannot alter it.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At 18th level, the dancer can choose any one special material or alignment that overcomes damage reduction (such as adamantine, cold iron, holy, or even lawful). Her aura now includes that material or alignment. Once she has made this choice, she cannot change it.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Offense"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1"},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[{"text":"The attacks performed by this Dancer is Magic Damage.","subTarget":"melee"},{"text":"Level 12: The attacks performed by this Dancer is aligned with either axis of the dancer for the purposes of bypassing Damage Reduction","subTarget":"melee"},{"text":"Level 18: The dancer can choose what material type their melee attacks are.","subTarget":"melee"}],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags"